# Ebb & Bloom - Agent Rules

## Project Overview
Law-based multi-agent universe simulator. Start at t=0 (Big Bang), watch emergence.

## Key Principles
1. **Bottom-up emergence** - Molecular → Stars → Galaxies → Cosmic web
2. **Yuka decides everything** - No forcing positions, counts, timing
3. **EntropyAgent governs** - Top-level thermodynamics (lightweight)
4. **Legal Brokers mediate** - All spawning/decisions validated by laws

## Architecture
```
EntropyAgent (universe thermodynamics, ~10 ops/frame)
  ↓ sets T, ρ, expansion
DensityAgents (collapse decisions)
  ↓ form
StellarAgents (fusion, supernova)
  ↓ create
PlanetaryAgents (atmosphere, life)
  ↓ spawn
CreatureAgents (survival, goals)
```

